    {
      "text": "A 4-year-old boy weighing 18 kg is admitted for minor elective surgery. According to the Holliday-Segar method, what is his estimated daily fluid requirement?",
      "options": [
        {
          "label": "A",
          "text": "1300 mL",
          "correct": false
        },
        {
          "label": "B",
          "text": "1400 mL",
